commit.message:
Bulletproofs and Public TX

This release rebases the core code to 13.0.4 It also changes the proof of work algorithm to Cryptonight V8 (CNv2), enables bulletproofs, enables public transactions (read more about public transactions on our whitepaper section on x-cash.org) and a fixed ringsize of 21.
